{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/post/my-hero-academia-live-action-legendary/","result":{"data":{"wordpressPost":{"title":"My Hero Academia Live Action Tengah Digarap Studio Legendary?","content":"<p>Tahun 2005 lalu, Disney pernah merilis film berjudul Sky High. Dalam film ini, anak-anak berkekuatan super dididik di sebuah sekolah untuk menjadi seorang <em>superhero</em> maupun <em>sidekick</em> mereka. Sky High mendapatkan respon yang baik, dan cukup untuk menutup biaya produksinya. Namun nampaknya Sky High yang konon tengah disiapkan sekuelnya sejak tahun 2016 ini akan menghadapi musuh baru dalam ranah film sekolah <em>superhero</em>: film My Hero Academia <em>live action!</em></p>\n<div id=\"attachment_51401\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-51401\" data-attachment-id=\"51401\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/my-hero-academia-live-action-legendary/attachment/01-my-hero-academia-live-action/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/01-my-hero-academia-live-action.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"01-my-hero-academia-live-action\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/01-my-hero-academia-live-action-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/01-my-hero-academia-live-action.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-51401\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/01-my-hero-academia-live-action.jpg\" alt=\"Sumber: VIZ\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/01-my-hero-academia-live-action.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/01-my-hero-academia-live-action-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-51401\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: VIZ</p></div>\n<p><em>Manga</em> karangan Kohei Horikoshi ini memang tengah mengalami masa-masa emasnya. Petualangan Deku bersama kawan-kawan sekolahnya untuk menjadi sosok <em>superhero</em> terhebat memang terlihat mirip Sky High, namun My Hero Academia punya <em>twist</em>-nya sendiri yang membuat <em>manga</em> ini menarik. Setelah sukses di media <em>anime</em> dan <em>manga</em>, merilis film perdananya, bahkan punya kolaborasi sendiri dengan film The Avengers, kali ini beredar kabar bahwa adaptasi film <em>live action</em>nya tengah dijajaki oleh studio Hollywood.</p>\n<p>Dilansir dari Variety, dikabarkan studio Legendary akan menggarap My Hero <em>Academia live action</em> ini. Statusnya saat ini masih mengumpulkan kru dan staf yang akan terlibat dalam proyek ini. Alex Garcia dan Jay Ashenfelter akan menjadi produser eksekutif, dan Yoritomi Ryosuke akan menjadi koordinator dari penerbit My Hero Academia, Shuheisha. Belum diketahui seberapa jauh Horikoshi terlibat dalam tim produksinya.</p>\n<p><strong>Baca Juga:Â <a href=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/avengers-my-hero-academia-crossover/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Kolaborasi Avengers dan My Hero Academia Adalah Crossover Superhero Paling Ambisius</a></strong></p>\n<div id=\"attachment_51402\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-51402\" data-attachment-id=\"51402\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/my-hero-academia-live-action-legendary/attachment/02-my-hero-academia-live-action/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/02-my-hero-academia-live-action.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"02-my-hero-academia-live-action\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/02-my-hero-academia-live-action-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/02-my-hero-academia-live-action.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-51402\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/02-my-hero-academia-live-action.jpg\" alt=\"Sumber: AMC Theatres\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/02-my-hero-academia-live-action.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/02-my-hero-academia-live-action-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-51402\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: AMC Theatres</p></div>\n<p>Mengangkat My Hero Academia ke dalam format film <em>live action</em> bukan sebuah keputusan yang random. 19 volume <em>manga</em> telah terjual sebanyak 17 juta kopi dan tersebar di seluruh dunia. <em>Manga</em> ini juga memenangkan penghargaan Sugoi Japan Award di tahun 2017. <em>Anime</em>nya sudah tayang sepanjang 3 <em>season</em> dan penayangan filmnya pun masih membekas di benak para fans seluruh dunia. Sah-sah saja jika Legendary ingin menyadur My Hero Academia menjadi film live action. Apalagi demam superhero masih melanda khalayak film dunia, apalagi film Avengers 4 sedang diproduksi.</p>\n<p>My Hero Academia <em>live action</em> bukan satu-satunya film Legendary yang digarap dari IP Jepang. Studio milik Wanda Group dari Cina ini juga tengah memproduksi film <em>kaiju</em> Godzilla: King of the Monsters dan Godzilla VS Kong; serta Pokemon: Detective Pikachu yang dibintangi Ryan Reynolds.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_51403\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-51403\" data-attachment-id=\"51403\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/my-hero-academia-live-action-legendary/attachment/03-my-hero-academia-live-action/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/03-my-hero-academia-live-action.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"03-my-hero-academia-live-action\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/03-my-hero-academia-live-action-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/03-my-hero-academia-live-action.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-51403\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/03-my-hero-academia-live-action.jpg\" alt=\"Sumber: IGN\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/03-my-hero-academia-live-action.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/03-my-hero-academia-live-action-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-51403\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: IGN</p></div>\n<p>Akankah film My Hero Academia <em>live action</em> menyaingi Sky High, atau justru jadi satu lagi adaptasi Hollywood yang gagal layaknya Dragon Ball Evolution? Mari kita pantau, mudah-mudahan jadinya nggak seperti gambar <em>banner</em> di atas ya! Sambil menunggu, kamu juga bisa baca berbagai komik <em>action</em> di <a href=\"https://www.ciayo.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">web komik gratis</a> CIAYO Comics! Klik gambar di bawah untuk mulai baca komiknya sekarang.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.ciayo.com/id/genre/action\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><img data-attachment-id=\"50177\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/karakter-metal-gear-solid-berkesan/attachment/print-8/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/Banner-Komik-Action.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1534763889&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;Print&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Banner Komik Action CIAYO Comics\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/Banner-Komik-Action-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/Banner-Komik-Action.jpg\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-50177\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/Banner-Komik-Action.jpg\" alt=\"Banner Komik Action\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/Banner-Komik-Action.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/Banner-Komik-Action-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /></a></p>\n"}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"id":"2a64f035-0179-5960-b254-ccc28ddcd66f"}}}